flowchart LR
    Graph[(asset_graph snapshot)] --> Engine[AttackGraphEngine]
    Engine --> Paths[Attack path discovery]
    Paths --> Risk[Risk scoring + severity]
    Risk --> Persist[(attack_paths table)]
    API[/GET /api/v1/attack-paths/] --> Persist
    Persist --> APIResp[AttackPathsResponse]
    APIResp --> UI[Threats Graph UI]
    Engine -->|missing node| Warn[NRVQ-GRP-11010 warning]
    Persist -->|db/session error| Err[NRVQ-API-7051-ERR]
